content.rendered:
Directed by Harsh Chhaya

Written by Harsh Chhaya

Cast Vinay Pathak (Ravinder Sharma). Suneeta Sengupta (Anuradha Sharma). Alka Amin (Kadhambhari Shrama). Manoj Pahwa (Jeetendar Sharma) . Dolly Ahluwalia (Lalita). Vicky Arora (Alok Sharma). Nagesh Bhonsle (ASI Dileep Jadhav). Birendar (Devendar Sharma). Kishore Chougule (Ganpat). Daljeet Singh Gujral (Aaditya). Deepak Kalra (Adityas father). Sanah Kapoor (Nayantara Sharma / Rosy). Nabeel Mirajkar (Amit Sharma (as Nabeel Ahmed)). Mayur More (Sharad). Seema Pahwa (Sushila Sharma). Prathamesh Parab (Rocky Dilwala). Ayush Saxena (Young devinder). Basu Soni (Deepak). Sultan Warsi

Language Hindi

Producers Meenakshi Pandey. Abhinandan Patidar. Amrit Sethia

Production Welcome Friends Production
